                <mxCell id="2PDZF1GC5zl0V-HgSjp5-4" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;799&quot; data-end=&quot;811&quot;&gt;do...while&lt;/code&gt; — executa pelo menos uma vez&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Diferença principal:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;O código roda ANTES de verificar a condição&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
